      • onStartCapture

        boolean onStartCapture(int numTiles,
                       int tileWidth,
                       int tileHeight,
                       int fullWidth,
                       int fullHeight)
        Capture process started - this is where you would create your destination file based on the arguments provided
        Parameters:
        numTiles - The total number of tiles being captured
        tileWidth - Tile width in pixels
        tileHeight - Tile height in pixels
        fullWidth - Full capture width in pixels
        fullHeight - Full capture height in pixels
        Returns:
        True to continue, false to stop
